## Excel chaos
- Data locked in inflexible and expensive single-purpose silos
- Untrustworthy or missing data
- Frustrated analysts and data scientists circumventing you with shadow IT
- An odd assortment of proprietary products and services requiring integration
- Lagging behind, always trying to catch up and meet business requirements

